<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="whisper-v">whisper <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'wɪspə(r)/    美 /'wɪspər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>低声讲：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>James leaned over <strong>to</strong> <strong>whisper</strong> something to Michael.
詹姆斯俯身跟迈克尔低声说了点什么。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You’ll have to whisper or he’ll hear you. 
你得小声说，否则他会听到的。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>What are you girls <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (耳语) about?  （2012 全国）  </li>
<li>Mum whispered<strong><em>_</em></strong>__ us, “Be quiet! Your little sister’s sleeping.”   </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. whispering  2. to   </p></div>